# Android
android/.gradle
android/captures/
android/local.properties
**/android/**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.java

# IMPORTANT: gradle-wrapper.jar must NOT be gitignored.
# It is a small (~44 KB) bootstrap binary that Gradle needs to launch itself.
# Without it the build fails with ClassNotFoundException: GradleWrapperMain.
# The file is regenerated by the CI workflow if it is absent, but committing
# it avoids the extra download step on every clean build.
# !android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar  ← uncomment if you want to commit the JAR

